content.body: Philadelphia-based mega-restaurateur Stephen Starr hits it out of the park with this animated neighborhood pizzeria on Headhouse Square, where the acclaimed Neapolitan-style pies come out of an 850º wood-burning oven, but the classic antipasti and pastas are so good that you might even save the pizza for next time.
content.name: why_we_like_it

about.body: Our corner pizzeria offers families a warm, and welcoming atmosphere to enjoy gourmet Neopolitan-inspired pizza, antipasti, pastas, accompanied by an approachable beverage list. The focus of the room is our gorgeous wood-burning oven where every pizza is made fresh to order.
